Hey y'all! Made a replica of the space launch system block 1 crew using stock parts, impossible innovations, and tweakscale. She performs nicely, and has a max reentry speed of 3,567 m/s (yes i can be that exact... sorry to gelfrey, bobby, and jorbald...(May they rest in peace)). Pics below + KerbalX .craft.

https://kerbalx.com/eva_reentry/SLS-orion
